article.description: Tanisha Wright had 23 points in No. 7 Penn State's 69-56 victory over Kansas State (No. 8 ESPN/USA Today; No. 9 AP) on Saturday in the championship game of the Junkanoo Shoot-out.
article.headline: Wright leads Penn State with 23
article.linkText: No. 7 Nittany Lions take Junkanoo Jam title
article.story:
FREEPORT, Bahamas (AP) -- Tanisha Wright had 23 points in No. 7
Penn State's 69-56 victory over No. 9 Kansas on Saturday in the
championship game of the Junkanoo Shoot-out .

Jess Strom added 15 points and had six assists for Penn State
(3-1), Nicole Ohlde had 15 points and 11 rebounds, and Kelly
Mazzante finished with 16 points.

Megan Mahoney led Kansas State (2-2) with 15 points and seven
rebounds, and Kendra Wecker added 13 points and 10 rebounds.
